["Zden\u011bk \u0160pinar (1916 \u2013 1995) was a Czech paleontologist and author. He was renowned in the field for popularising vertebrate paleontology. He specialised in the paleontology of amphibians, especially anurans. Many of his studies remain heavily cited. He is also known for a scientific collaboration with painter Zden\u011bk Burian.","This Czech biographical article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]